{"tid":1116491,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"Sammi原來係唐朝公主 老鼠安係吐蕃將軍","createTime":"2019-04-20T04:49:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T05:34:28.000Z","uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"333861fb5c068e8a64931dde0c37b227e270df9c","tid":1116491,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:49:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1425546?from=fb_et_star\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1425546%3Ffrom%3Dfb_et_star&d=v6UOKjiqNHu3M1gE0B2GLClkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=8ef4e424\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1425546?from=fb_et_star</a><br />\n<br />\n許志安日前被爆背著鄭秀文與港姐黃心穎偷情，命理師小孟老師分析他們的前世今生，透露鄭秀文前世為唐朝公主，許志安是吐蕃將軍，黃心穎則是鄭秀文的丫嬛。小孟老師表示，他們三人早在前世就有所關聯，鄭秀文原先將與許志安結婚，卻因醉酒與丫鬟發生關係，指出他們從前世就有所糾葛。<br />\n<br />\n小孟老師透露，唐朝為了與吐蕃更多交流，將公主嫁入吐蕃國，不過嫁入的鄭秀文不喜歡國王，反而愛上將軍許志安，兩人也越愛越激烈。然而，丫鬟黃心穎也愛慕將軍，某天趁著將軍喝醉闖入，穿著鄭秀文的衣服、假裝是鄭秀文的聲音與將軍發生關係，醒來後的將軍也嚇到。<br />\n<br />\n不久後丫鬟懷孕，吐蕃國王讓許志安與黃心穎結婚，也傷透了鄭秀文的心。黃心穎以為能就此能鎖住許志安，豈料許志安誓言要幫皇帝奪下其他領土，卻就此天人永隔。許志安戰死前留下一封書信給鄭秀文，內容寫到，「今生無緣成夫妻，來世再結連理，生生世世不分離。」<br />\n小孟老師幫鄭秀文與許志安抽塔羅牌為「太陽牌正位」，顯示兩人不會分離，鄭會原諒、許會痛改前非，二年後東山再起，黃心穎則會跌入谷底。另外此牌也說明，許志安並不是第一次有桃花，但鄭秀文包容心強，也怕影響兩人演藝生涯，小孟老師更直言：「背後有高人指點這次事件不可分離，要兩人再重修舊好再創演藝高峰。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380ce1af9da6f1fff69eab707716d2da6ff7bb9f","tid":1116491,"uid":74696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:49:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3306de9f39dbab2658f6bb408e6c4b39af1f1f63","tid":1116491,"uid":220431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:50:44.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79fdfb0e685d420861431a8ba41be204441c0ed8","tid":1116491,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:55:18.000Z","msg":"笑撚死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769e81f908e5b4891dc98c96ebbd033b6cac7b6d","tid":1116491,"uid":39256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6770013fc97a0f05a9b373c4822e6800ba05e02b","tid":1116491,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:57:53.000Z","msg":"個公主同將軍叫咩名？名都冇點信？"},{"pid":"1fc0890645eda856fc56eb4225899721aa0fa973","tid":1116491,"uid":165619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:59:18.000Z","msg":"咁撚叻早幾年唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fbf354138cfcfa82b560c79cc1ac331f16ca75","tid":1116491,"uid":144464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T05:02:44.000Z","msg":"原來關係一早已經咁淫亂，老鼠安識食喎"},{"pid":"5a1a1a742c8bec19267f9db27fba28262c0fb295","tid":1116491,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6770013fc97a0f05a9b373c4822e6800ba05e02b","tid":1116491,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:57:53.000Z","msg":"個公主同將軍叫咩名？名都冇點信？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T05:04:58.000Z","msg":"長平公主係咩朝代㗎？"},{"pid":"9f61d50f23289e3ae6b2564d319dc8e5d616deca","tid":1116491,"uid":41154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-0